title: Blazing 5 – Week 6
itunes:title: Blazing 5 – Week 6
description:
Colin is off to his best ever start to a season with his Blazing 5 and he loves his week 6 picks.  RJ Bell of pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree and disagree with.  Plus, Colin includes a bonus 6th pick exclusive to this podcast not in his Blazing 5.
